      class  DblArray1Vector
      double[] implementation of VectorIntf.
      Methods in popt4jlib that return PoolableObjectIntf 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      PoolableObjectIntf DblArray1Vector.cloneObject()
      returns an unmanaged (ie not belonging to the thread-local object pool) DblArray1Vector object that is a cloned (deep) copy of the data in this object.
      PoolableObjectIntf PoolableObjectIntf.cloneObject()
      create a new un-managed object of same type as this object, for use by other threads as well.

    • Uses of PoolableObjectIntf in popt4jlib.NumberPartitioning

      Classes in popt4jlib.NumberPartitioning that implement PoolableObjectIntf 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  FNPTask
      class implements the CKK algorithm (Complete Karmarkar-Karp Algorithm) for 2-way Number Partitioning, due to Richard Korf (1997).
      (package private) class  ReleaseFNPTaskObject
      Encapsulates the requirement for calling the release() method of the PoolableObjectIntf interface, from a specific thread (the one that created the FNPTask object that it holds, as well as the object itself).
      Methods in popt4jlib.NumberPartitioning that return PoolableObjectIntf 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      PoolableObjectIntf FNPTask.cloneObject()
      returns an unmanaged (ie not belonging to the thread-local object pool) FNPTask object that is a cloned (deep) copy of the data in this object.
      PoolableObjectIntf ReleaseFNPTaskObject.cloneObject()
      returns an unmanaged (ie not belonging to the thread-local object pool) ReleaseFNPTaskObject object that is a cloned (deep) copy of the data in this object.
